{"id":149082,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/简讯：-李方平失踪超过24小时/","date":"2011-05-01T16:30:32Z","modified":"2011-05-01T16:30:32Z","title":"简讯： 李方平失踪超过24小时","content":"<div>\n<p>据网友转发的北京非盈利公益性机构益仁平中心负责人陆军发布的公告信说，北京海淀羊坊店派出所的值班警员4月30日上午受理了维权律师李方平家人对他的失踪报案。</p>\n<p>该告知信称，李方平失踪已经24小时仍没有音讯。</p>\n<p>此前，该中心曾发表公告说，李方平29日下午在该中心的楼下“被一批人带走”。而有网友表示，关注中国社会公益权利的李方平是被北京警方带走的。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/RXIMOjGqzT0uLyQazVeL6xpnsOE/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/RXIMOjGqzT0uLyQazVeL6xpnsOE/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/RXIMOjGqzT0uLyQazVeL6xpnsOE/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/RXIMOjGqzT0uLyQazVeL6xpnsOE/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/gClLRCi33Kw\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[14986,9378]}